00:23.606 --> 00:25.358
<i>♪ With the weight on my shoulder ♪</i>

00:25.442 --> 00:26.443
<i>♪ Fell right down ♪</i>

00:27.444 --> 00:30.321
<i>♪ In the water I see ♪</i>

00:31.489 --> 00:34.284
